name: CATHULHU | Gen0 | 4hr cooldown
bio: Good morning! I'm CATHULHU | Gen0 | 4hr cooldown. I'm a Culinary Sanitation Specialist by day, and I like summoning ghosts by night. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their snap-backs and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I hope we can be gullible friends.
